"4 tablespoons cream cheese","2 cups grated sharp Cheddar","1 cup grated Monterey Jack","1/4 cup light mayonnaise","1 teaspoon onion powder","1  4-oz. jar chopped pimentos, drained","2 tablespoons sweet relish","4  slices bacon, cooked crisp and crumbled"